<L>__{exterior doll shop night}
<A>__{we see madeleine, inside, painting a doll's face. louis and claudia arrive outside.}
<C>__{claudia}
<D>__{all her dolls resemble me.}
<B>__{pov}
<A>__{claudia's face, with the dolls in the background. the resemblance is uncanny.}
<C>__{claudia}
<D>__{are they my kind louis? dolls never change either.}
<C>__{louis}
<D>__{you are neither, claudia. now stop this }
<A>__{madeleine sees claudia from inside. she waves.}
<C>__{louis}
<D>__{you know her?}
<C>__{claudia}
<D>__{yes. should i take her, louis? among her dolls? make a doll of her in turn?}
<C>__{louis}
<D>__{come, claudia...}
<A>__{he takes her arm. but claudia shakes him off, and moves into the shop.}
